NAME

  Relations::Query v0.93

DESCRIPTION

  This module is for creating complex select SQL queries 
  using Relations.

COPYRIGHT

  Copyright 2001 GAF-3 Industries, Inc. All rights reserved.
  Written by George A. Fitch III (aka Gaffer), gaf3@gaf3.com

  This program is free software, you can redistribute it and/or modify it under
  the same terms as Perl istelf

INSTALlATION

  REQUIRED
 
    perl 5.004
    Relations >= 0.94

  WIN32 (Relations-Query-0.93.zip)

    Extract zip file into a directory and type

    ppm install Relations-Query.ppd

  UN*X (Relations-Query-0.93.tar.gz)

    Extract bundle into a directory and type

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install

TESTING

  After installing, run test.pl by typing 

    perl test.pl

  while in the installation directory.